ZH: 无所不在的科技已经改变了我们的生活方式。
EN: Technology, which is ubiquitous, has changed our way of life.

ZH: 现代社交媒体无所不在，人们可以随时随地与朋友保持联系。
EN: Modern social media is omnipresent, allowing people to stay connected with friends anytime, anywhere.

ZH: 污染已然成为一个无所不在的问题，我们需要采取行动保护环境。
EN: Pollution has become an omnipresent issue, and we need to take action to protect the environment.

ZH: 快餐店无所不在，但它们对我们的健康并不利。
EN: Fast food restaurants are everywhere, but they are not beneficial for our health.

ZH: 在互联网时代，假新闻无所不在，我们需要培养辨别信息真伪的能力。
EN: In the era of the Internet, fake news is omnipresent, and we need to cultivate the ability to discern the authenticity of information.

ZH: 塑料垃圾无所不在，给地球造成了巨大的环境问题。
EN: Plastic waste is omnipresent and has created significant environmental problems for the planet.

ZH: 经济全球化使跨国公司无所不在。
EN: Economic globalization has made multinational corporations ubiquitous.

ZH: 在电子商务的时代，网购无所不在。
EN: In the era of e-commerce, online shopping is everywhere.

ZH: 广告片已经成为电视和网络视频中无所不在的一部分。
EN: Advertisements have become an omnipresent part of television and online videos.

ZH: 无人机的应用正在成为现实生活中无所不在的一部分。
EN: The use of drones is becoming an omnipresent part of everyday life.

ZH: 社交媒体的广告已经无所不在，公司们借此推销产品。
EN: Advertisements on social media are ubiquitous, and companies use them to promote their products.

ZH: 在现代音乐中，电子音乐元素无所不在。
EN: Electronic music elements are omnipresent in modern music.

ZH: 网络游戏在年轻人的生活中无所不在。
EN: Online games are ubiquitous in the lives of young people.

ZH: 电影院无所不在，我们可以在几乎每个城市找到一家。
EN: Movie theaters are everywhere; we can find one in almost every city.

ZH: 少年儿童艺术活动无所不在，培养了他们的创造力和想象力。
EN: Art activities for children are omnipresent, nurturing their creativity and imagination.

ZH: 广播电台无所不在，我们可以随时收听到音乐和新闻。
EN: Radio stations are everywhere; we can listen to music and news anytime.

ZH: 快递服务已经无所不在，方便我们的日常生活。
EN: Delivery services are omnipresent, making our daily lives more convenient.

ZH: 网络支付已经无所不在，让人们更加便捷地进行金融交易。
EN: Online payment is everywhere, enabling people to conduct financial transactions more conveniently.

ZH: 地铁系统无所不在，成为城市交通的重要组成部分。
EN: Subway systems are ubiquitous and have become an integral part of urban transportation.

ZH: 移动电话已经无所不在，我们可以随时打电话或发信息。
EN: Mobile phones are everywhere, and we can make calls or send messages anytime.
